      <title><![CDATA[brief introduction of md grammer]]></title>
      <url>/2020/02/17/brief-introduction-of-md-grammer/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">main content: markdown gramer points to help you in writing beautiful md documents</span><br><span class="line">pay attention: only tested or checked right under os ubuntu and software Typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>[toc]</p>
<h1 id="enhance"><a href="#enhance" class="headerlink" title="enhance"></a>enhance</h1><p>1.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* ** ***: 包围内容分别斜体，粗体，粗斜体</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: <em>斜体</em>, <strong>粗体</strong>, <strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong><br>2. </p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~words~~ &lt;u&gt;words&lt;&#x2F;u&gt;: 包围分别为删除线与下划线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: <del>删除线</del>, <u>下划线</u><br>3.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~ ^: 包围内容分别为下标与上标，如：H~2~0, X^3^</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: H<del>2</del>0, X^3^<br>4.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:emoji name: 显示emoji图像，如:happy:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: :happy: :smile:<br>5. </p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">==: 包围内容高亮</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: ==高亮==<br>6.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`: 包围显示效果如下,可用于在文字中显示函数调用等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: <code>printf()</code><br>7.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">"字体名"</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">12</span>&gt;</span></span>words<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg: <font color="#0099ff" size="3" face="黑体">黑体</font><br>8. </p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^脚注名</span>]: <span class="link">需要使用'[^脚注名]: 脚注内容'指明脚注对应内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>eg:  md[^markdown]<br>[^markdown]: markdown是一门文本标记语音</p>
<h1 id="label"><a href="#label" class="headerlink" title="label"></a>label</h1><p>1.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span>/+++/---: 生成水平线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>2.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;: 引用标示，可多个连用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>3.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>: 代码块标示，后续可制定代码语言类型（有美化效果）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>4.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---: 在文档最开始使用，显示一个记录文字元信息的区块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>5.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">toc</span>]: <span class="link">自动生成目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>6.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">link name</span>](<span class="link">link addr "title"</span>): 插入连接，鼠标悬浮显示title内容，点击跳转link addr. 可用[<span class="string">link name</span>][<span class="symbol">link</span>]+[<span class="string">link</span>]: link addr "title"显示同样效果，此外link addr可以是页面内的锚点[<span class="string">link</span>](<span class="link">#anchor name "title"</span>)，其中锚点anchor name可以是标题锚点或者制定<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span>标签的id</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>7.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">addr</span>&gt;</span></span>: 使用该方式使得点击文字有跳到链接位置效果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>8.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">img</span>](<span class="link">path name "title"</span>): 与上方链接类似</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>9.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>*  + or -: 前者为有序列表，后三个均为无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>10.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[ ]  - [x]: 显示单选框</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>11. </p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|column 1|column 2|column 3|</span><br><span class="line">|:-------|:------:|-------:|</span><br><span class="line">|c1<span class="emphasis">_value|c2_</span>value|c3_value|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>12.</p>
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">#: 标题，可多个，分别代表h1, h2, h3等等</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>]]></content>
      
