<h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">bash</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

